One may test the program using the following format:

dna_database = "input file path";
dna_sequence = "sequence of A, T, G, and Cs"
std::string expected = "name"
if main(dna_database, dna_sequence) == expected:
  print("passed")

One may test specific methods using the following format:

# testing the longest_consecutive_str() method
target_sequence = "AATG"
dna_sequence = "AATAATTAATTAATTAAATGAATGAATGAATGAATGAATGTATTATCATTAAATGT"
expected = 6
if LongestConsecutiveSTR(dna_sequence, target_sequence) == expected:
  print("passed")
